dct_title_s: Spain 1:7,500. Malaga city plan. A.M.S. M981
dct_description_sm: AMS 1. Alternate title: Malaga city plan. Copied from Spanish H. O. chart no. 123 B, 1936. Revised in part from R.A.F. aerial photographs, 1941- 42. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. Iberian Peninsula Zone grid. Depth shown by soundings in meters.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
